            <title><![CDATA[Battlefield 6 Beta Eclipses Call Of Duty Player Record On Steam]]></title>
            <link>https://www.gamespot.com/articles/battlefield-6-beta-eclipses-call-of-duty-player-record-on-steam/1100-6533822/?ftag=CAD-01-10abi2f</link>
