      </div>
<p>While this is a cause for high-fives at EA, it remains to be seen just how much of the buzz from the Battlefield 6 open beta will translate into actual sales of the game. <a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/call-of-duty-and-battlefield-are-getting-new-games-in-the-same-year-for-the-first-time-since-2021/1100-6533628/">Battlefield 6 is also going up against its old rival Call of Duty this year</a>, and Activision's annual series is expected to be one of the best-selling games of 2025. Since the Activision-published game will also be a day-one release through Xbox Game Pass, it'll also have a sizable advantage over Battlefield 6.</p><p>The Battlefield 6 beta has been positively received as well, with players praising the grounded approach to warfare, <a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/all-game-modes-in-battlefield-6-explained/1100-6533786/">the various game modes on offer</a>, and <a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/battlefield-6-aims-to-bring-back-comprehensive-destruction-from-much-loved-bad-company-2/1100-6533686/">destruction physics</a> that'll make Bad Company 2 fans smile.</p><p>There have been some issues along the way, as naturally, <a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/the-battlefield-6-open-beta-is-apparently-already-dealing-with-cheaters/1100-6533808/">cheaters have surfaced</a> on PC and have found a way around EA's <a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/battlefield-6-how-to-turn-on-secure-boot-on-pc/1100-6533761/">Secure Boot technology</a>. <a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/enabling-secure-boot-for-battlefield-6-is-turning-into-a-nightmare-for-some/1100-6533811/">Enabling the anti-cheat software has also become a problem</a> for several players.</p><p>To prep for the second open beta this weekend, you can check out our features on <a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/battlefield-6-how-to-turn-on-secure-boot-on-pc/1100-6533761/">how to secure boot Battlefield 6</a> on PC, <a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/best-controller-settings-in-battlefield-6/1100-6533742/">the best controller settings to use</a>, and <a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/battlefield-6-heres-how-ai-bots-work-in-the-open-beta/1100-6533757/">how AI bots work</a>.</p>
  
                        
    
        
        
  
